title: **AVAILABLE RENT TO OWN**
posting_body: ['The Rent to Own Program is a great option if you:', '• Want to live in a single-family home, in a great community with quality schools', '• Are a first-time homebuyer who’s cautious about buying a home now, but may want to buy in the future', '• Are a home seeker in the process of relocating but aren’t sure where you want to settle down', '• Can’t obtain a mortgage right now', '• Simply want to live in a quality home', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program:', 'Lateefah Mathews, Realtor®', 'Lease Purchase Specialist', 'REAL BROKER LLC', 'Basic Requirements to Qualify for the Program:', '-$50,000+ annual household income', '-600+ MINIMUM credit score (No Exceptions At All!)', '-Self-employment, SSI, Child support, VA, accepted', '-Stable employment', '-No evictions within the last year', '-No felony convictions within the last 4 years', '-No pending bankruptcy', '-No Credit Impact to you at all!', '-LOW APPLICATION FEE...', 'NO CREDIT IMPACT...!', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program:', '<URL>', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
